headline: Valero price target raised to $165 from $164 at Raymond James
summary: Raymond James analyst Justin Jenkins raised the firm’s price target on Valero (VLO) to $165 from $164 and keeps a Strong Buy rating on the shares. Valero remains one of the firm’s favorite ways to play higher refining margins, with the addition of a material head start in key renewable themes, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
